<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٠ -<span class="c5"> وَأَنْشَدَنِي:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مَنْ حَمِدَ النَّاسَ وَلَمْ يَبْلُهُمْ ... ثُمَّ بَلاهُمْ ذَمَّ مَنْ يَحْمَدُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَصَارَ بِالْوَحْدَةِ مُسْتَأْنِسًا ... يُوحِشُهُ الأَقْرَبُ وَالأَبْعَدُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>